What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Thermal Transfer Tapes Market?

Market Analysis and Insights

Thermal Transfer Tapes Market

Data Bridge Market Research analyses that the thermal transfer tapes market will project a CAGR of 10.60% for the forecast period of 2022-2029. Rising focus on the packaging product innovations and technological advancements by the manufacturers, growth and expansion of packaging industry especially in the developing economies such as India and China, surging demand for innovative packaging solutions that are developed with advanced and innovative methods of manufacturing, growing usage of thermal transfer tapes for aerospace and defines applications and increased personal disposable income are the factors driving the growth of thermal transfer tapes market.

From the name itself, it is clear that the thermal transfer tapes are the packaging solutions that offer high performance thermal conductivity with a well-balanced double sided acrylic adhesive system. The thermal transfer tapes are a far superior option when it comes to heat transfer or thermal conductivity.

Rising urbanization, modernization, and globalization is driving the growth in the market value. Growing product innovations by the manufacturing industry, surging awareness about the benefits of thermal transfer tapes, rising demand for electronic gadgets and surging development in the flexible packaging solutions will further induce growth in the market value. Surging research and development proficiencies, growing focus of the manufacturers on minimize the production cost without compromising with the quality, surging demand for prevalence for electric vehicles especially in the western economies, growing technological advancements in the packaging equipment and technology to accommodate a diversified range of products and increased proliferation of e-commerce industry are some other market growth determinants.

However, supply chain disruptions owing to the covid-19 pandemic will create hindrances for the market growth rate. Fluctuations in the prices of raw materials will further dampen the market growth rate. Large scale availability of alternatives in the market will hamper the market growth rate.

